## Overview

This file is the **implementation file** (`.cpp`) of a C++ Object-Oriented Attendance Management System. It provides the actual working code (definitions) for all the classes and functions that are *declared* in the corresponding header file `AttendanceSystem.h`. Think of the header file as a blueprint or table of contents, and this `.cpp` file as the full, detailed book. The system manages students, teachers, and an admin, supports file saving/loading, and can generate an HTML dashboard.

